        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h5 id="一、名词解释"><a href="#一、名词解释" class="headerlink" title="一、名词解释"></a>一、名词解释</h5><p>关系：一张表<a id="more"></a></p><p>元组：关系中的行</p><p>属性：关系中的列</p><p>笛卡尔积：设A,B为集合，用A中元素为第一元素，B中元素为第二元素构成有序对，所有这样的有序对组成的集合叫做A与B的笛卡尔积，记作AxB。公式表示为：</p><p>A×B={(x,y)|x∈A∧y∈B}  (<strong>A与B的所有组合都写出来</strong>)。</p><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="275" style="border-collapse: collapse;table-layout:fixed;width:208pt"> <col width="53" style="mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:1696;width:40pt"> <col width="33" style="mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:1056;width:25pt"> <col width="53" style="mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:1696;width:40pt"> <col width="30" style="mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:960;width:23pt"> <col width="53" span="2" style="mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:1696; width:40pt"> <tr height="33" style="mso-height-source:userset;height:24.95pt">  <td height="33" class="xl7113044" width="53" style="height:24.95pt;width:40pt">A</td>  <td class="xl7313044" width="33" style="border-left:none;width:25pt">　</td>  <td class="xl7113044" width="53" style="border-left:none;width:40pt">B</td>  <td rowspan="5" class="xl6713044" width="30" style="border-bottom:1.0pt solid #DFE2E5;  width:23pt">　</td>  <td colspan="2" class="xl6913044" width="106" style="border-right:1.0pt solid #DFE2E5;  border-left:none;width:80pt">A×B</td> </tr> <tr height="33" style="mso-height-source:userset;height:24.95pt">  <td height="33" class="xl6613044" width="53" style="height:24.95pt;border-top:none;  width:40pt">a</td>  <td rowspan="4" class="xl6813044" width="33" style="border-bottom:1.0pt solid #DFE2E5;  width:25pt">　</td>  <td class="xl6613044" width="53" style="border-top:none;border-left:none;  width:40pt">c</td>  <td class="xl6613044" width="53" style="border-top:none;border-left:none;  width:40pt">a</td>  <td class="xl6613044" width="53" style="border-top:none;border-left:none;  width:40pt">c</td> </tr> <tr height="33" style=